  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Cozy Desktop Konbini</u></strong> is a cozy and relaxing idle game about managing a Konbini that stays at the bottom of your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/851affd881fdcd3e5702bb9a67968dc0.poster.avif?t=1744961576\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/851affd881fdcd3e5702bb9a67968dc0.webm?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/851affd881fdcd3e5702bb9a67968dc0.mp4?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Everything is Automated</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your Konbini runs smoothly on its own—restock shelves, serve customers, and earn money, all while you focus on other tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multitasking</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This idle game sits at the bottom of your screen, letting you manage your shop while studying, working, or just relaxing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Decorate your Konbini</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your tiny Konbini with shelves, displays, and decorations to create the coziest shopping experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/7c69cd7e3ebd81c9d3b08ae345fb9011.poster.avif?t=1744961576\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/7c69cd7e3ebd81c9d3b08ae345fb9011.webm?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/7c69cd7e3ebd81c9d3b08ae345fb9011.mp4?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock New Products and Buildings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your Konbini with new shelves, vending machines, and unique products to attract more customers and grow your business!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make a tiny gym</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some exercise wouldn’t hurt, right? Add a small gym section to your Konbini and let your customers work out while they shop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/543561577e3675411d38a1945cda7ca6.poster.avif?t=1744961576\" width=600 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/543561577e3675411d38a1945cda7ca6.webm?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/543561577e3675411d38a1945cda7ca6.mp4?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s Perfect for You, If You</strong> :</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍙 Need a little break from your work</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍙 Need a little dopamine boost</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍙 Love decorating and customizing your own space</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍙 Enjoy cozy, low-maintenance games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍙 Appreciate chill vibes and relaxing lofi music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Cozy Desktop Konbini</u></strong> is a cozy and relaxing idle game about managing a Konbini that stays at the bottom of your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/851affd881fdcd3e5702bb9a67968dc0.poster.avif?t=1744961576\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/851affd881fdcd3e5702bb9a67968dc0.webm?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/851affd881fdcd3e5702bb9a67968dc0.mp4?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Everything is Automated</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your Konbini runs smoothly on its own—restock shelves, serve customers, and earn money, all while you focus on other tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multitasking</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This idle game sits at the bottom of your screen, letting you manage your shop while studying, working, or just relaxing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Decorate your Konbini</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your tiny Konbini with shelves, displays, and decorations to create the coziest shopping experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/7c69cd7e3ebd81c9d3b08ae345fb9011.poster.avif?t=1744961576\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503230/extras/7c69cd7e3ebd81c9d3b08ae345fb9011.webm?t=1744961576\" type=\"video/webm;